				<div class="body">
					<p>I found that with tip number one I also needed to implement a debug_backtrace (otherwise my debug info referrenced the bootstrap file rather than the place where I was calling my debug/die function):</p>
<p>function d($data)<br />
{</br><br />
    $backtrace = debug_backtrace();</br><br />
    debug('File: ' . $backtrace[0]['file'] . ' Line: ' . $backtrace[0]['line']);</br><br />
    unset($backtrace);</br><br />
    die(debug($data));</br><br />
}</br></p>
<p>Of course debug_backtrace is PHP5 specific.</p>
				</div>
